dc_description_s: This data layer represents roads for Polk County, Wisconsin in 2011. [Line centerline map features of the roads within Polk County Wisconsin. Each segment of the road includes the road name, address ranges, road code, and zip code.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data for this county, please visit: https://www.polkcountywi.gov/government/divisions_and_departments/environmental_services_division/land_information/gis_data_portal.php
